    "Speci cally, it showed high agreement in Recruitment and Arm/Intervention, with accuracy of 88% and 93%, respectively.",
    "However, it demonstrated discrepancies in designing Eligibility Criteria and Outcomes Measurement, with accuracy of 55% and 53%, respectively.",
